msgid "swab"
msgstr "swab"

#: ../../S/swab.rst:7
msgid "/swob/"
msgstr "/swob/"

#: ../../S/swab.rst:9
msgid ""
"[From the mnemonic for the :ref:`PDP-11` ‘SWAp Byte’ instruction, as "
"immortalized in the :manpage:`dd(1)` option :code:`conv=swab` (see "
":ref:`dd`\\)]"
msgstr ""
"[\\ :ref:`PDP-11`\\ の‘SWAp Byte’命令のニーモニックから。\\ :manpage:`dd(1)`\\ のオプション\\ "
":code:`conv=swab`\\ で不朽となった(\\ :ref:`dd`\\ を参照)]"

#: ../../S/swab.rst:11
msgid "vt\\. To solve the :ref:`NUXI-problem` by swapping bytes in a file"
msgstr "他動詞 ファイル中のバイトを入れ替えて\\ :ref:`NUXI-problem`\\ を解決すること"

#: ../../S/swab.rst:14
msgid ""
"n\\. The program in V7 Unix used to perform this action, or anything "
"functionally equivalent to it. See also :ref:`big-endian`\\, :ref:`little-"
"endian`\\, :ref:`middle-endian`\\, :ref:`bytesexual`\\."
msgstr ""
"名詞 V7 Unixでこの動作を行うのに使われたプログラム、または機能的にそれと等価なもの。\\ :ref:`big-endian`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`little-endian`\\ 、\\ :ref:`middle-endian`\\ 、\\ :ref:`bytesexual`\\ "
"も参照。"
